OL,5, A practising barrister has been fined  
OL,6, after speaking in a German accent and  
OL,7, raising his hand in a Nazi salute in   
OL,8, court.                                 
OL,10,FThomas David Davidson was at Salisbury 
OL,11,FMagistrates' Court on 7 February 2022  
OL,12,Fwhen he engaged in the "seriously      
OL,13,Foffensive and discreditable" conduct,  
OL,14,Fthe Bar Standards Board (BSB) said.    
OL,16,FMr Davidson - who is based in London - 
OL,17,Fwas fined #250 by the regulator on 21  
OL,18,FNovember.                              
OL,20,FHe must also pay costs of #1,750.      
